q = load "PROPOSITION_SCORE"; q = filter q by 'Customer' in {{selection(Customer_37)}} && 'Product_category' in {{selection(Product_category_18)}} && 'Channel' in {{ selection(Channel_35) }} && 'Sales_region' in {{ selection(Region_34) }} && X4P_5P_6P in {{ selection(X4P_5P_6P_32) }} &&  'Country' in {{ selection(Country_29) }} && 'Customer' in {{ selection(Customer_28) }} && 'Commune' in {{ selection(Commune_40) }} && 'Customer_type' in {{ selection(Customer_type_13) }} && 'Trade_Format' in {{ selection(Trade_Format_9) }} && 'Sales_area' in {{ selection(Sales_area_7) }} && 'Sales_territory' in {{ selection(Sales_territory_8) }} && 'Field_Execution_Manager' in {{ selection(Field_Execution_Manager_44) }} && 'Store_Operations_Manager' in {{ selection(Store_Operations_Manager_45) }} && 'Field_Sales_Manager' in {{selection(Field_Sales_Manager_46) }} && 'Product_division' in {{ selection(Product_division_17) }} && 'Local_Outlet_Name' in {{ selection(Local_Outlet_Name_47) }} && 'Subchannel' in {{ selection(Subchannel_11) }} && 'Top_Customer' in {{ selection(Top_Customer_41) }}; q = filter q by date('Date_of_audit_Year', 'Date_of_audit_Month', 'Date_of_audit_Day') in ["6 months ago".."6 months ago"]; q = group q by ('Product_category', 'SKU_ID', 'SKU'); q = foreach q generate 'Product_category' as 'Product Category', 'SKU_ID' as 'SKU ID', 'SKU' as 'SKU', avg('CTA_Compliant') as 'lastCTACompliant';

q = load "PROPOSITION_SCORE"; q = filter q by 'Customer' in {{selection(Customer_37)}} && 'Product_category' in {{selection(Product_category_18)}} && 'Channel' in {{ selection(Channel_35) }} && 'Sales_region' in {{ selection(Region_34) }} && X4P_5P_6P in {{ selection(X4P_5P_6P_32) }} &&  'Country' in {{ selection(Country_29) }} && 'Customer' in {{ selection(Customer_28) }} && 'Commune' in {{ selection(Commune_40) }} && 'Customer_type' in {{ selection(Customer_type_13) }} && 'Trade_Format' in {{ selection(Trade_Format_9) }} && 'Sales_area' in {{ selection(Sales_area_7) }} && 'Sales_territory' in {{ selection(Sales_territory_8) }} && 'Field_Execution_Manager' in {{ selection(Field_Execution_Manager_44) }} && 'Store_Operations_Manager' in {{ selection(Store_Operations_Manager_45) }} && 'Field_Sales_Manager' in {{selection(Field_Sales_Manager_46) }} && 'Product_division' in {{ selection(Product_division_17) }} && 'Local_Outlet_Name' in {{ selection(Local_Outlet_Name_47) }} && 'Subchannel' in {{ selection(Subchannel_11) }} && 'Top_Customer' in {{ selection(Top_Customer_41) }};cur = filter q by date('Date_of_audit_Year', 'Date_of_audit_Month', 'Date_of_audit_Day') in ["5 months ago".."5 months ago"];last = filter q by date('Date_of_audit_Year', 'Date_of_audit_Month', 'Date_of_audit_Day') in ["6 months ago".."6 months ago"]; diff = cogroup cur by ('CTA_Message') full, last by ('CTA_Message'); diff = foreach diff generate coalesce(cur::'CTA_Message',last::'CTA_Message') as 'CTA_Message', avg(cur.CTA_Compliant) as currentCTACompliant, avg(last.CTA_Compliant) as lastCTACompliant, (case when avg(cur.CTA_Compliant) is null then coalesce(0-avg(last.CTA_Compliant), 999) else coalesce(avg(cur.CTA_Compliant)-avg(last.CTA_Compliant),999) end) as 'ctaCompliantAverage';
